Metaspins API Documentation
STREAMER · JSON · READ-ONLY
Read-only leaderboard API. Pull ranked player wagering data for any UTC time range with a single GET request.
Endpoint
GET https://data.crossfade.gg/{slug}/{api_key}?from={unix_start}&to={unix_end}
Parameter
Description
slug
api_key
from / 
Public streamer slug (from your manager)
Secret key starting with 
to
cf_
Unix timestamp in seconds (UTC)
No auth headers — the key in the URL is your credential.
Example
Request
curl "https://data.crossfade.gg/your-slug/cf_YOUR_API_KEY?from=1782864000&to=1785542399"
